## Installation

**1. Clone**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/cloakedbyte/elite-clipboard.git
cd elite-clipboard
```

**2. Install Go dependencies**

```bash
go mod tidy
```

**3. Build**

```bash
mkdir -p bin
go build -o bin/elite-clipd ./cmd/daemon/
go build -o bin/ecb ./cmd/ecb/
go build -o bin/elite-tray ./cmd/tray/
```

**4. Install to PATH**

```bash
sudo ln -sf $(pwd)/bin/elite-clipd /usr/local/bin/elite-clipd
sudo ln -sf $(pwd)/bin/ecb /usr/local/bin/ecb
sudo ln -sf $(pwd)/bin/ecb-pick /usr/local/bin/ecb-pick
```

**5. Check your DISPLAY**

```bash
echo $DISPLAY
# usually :1 on Pop!_OS and Ubuntu
```

**6. Create daemon service at `~/.config/systemd/user/elite-clipboard.service`**

```ini
[Unit]
Description=elite-clipboard daemon
After=graphical-session.target
PartOf=graphical-session.target

[Service]
Type=simple
ExecStart=%h/elite-clipboard/bin/elite-clipd
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=3
StandardOutput=append:%h/.local/share/elite-clipboard/daemon.log
StandardError=append:%h/.local/share/elite-clipboard/daemon.log
Environment=DISPLAY=:1
Environment=XAUTHORITY=/home/YOUR_USERNAME/.Xauthority

[Install]
WantedBy=graphical-session.target
```

**7. Create tray service at `~/.config/systemd/user/elite-tray.service`**

```ini
[Unit]
Description=elite-clipboard tray
After=graphical-session.target elite-clipboard.service
Wants=elite-clipboard.service

[Service]
Type=simple
ExecStart=%h/elite-clipboard/bin/elite-tray
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=3
Environment=DISPLAY=:1
Environment=XAUTHORITY=/home/YOUR_USERNAME/.Xauthority

[Install]
WantedBy=graphical-session.target
```

Replace `YOUR_USERNAME` and `DISPLAY=:1` with your values.

**8. Enable and start**

```bash
systemctl --user daemon-reload
systemctl --user enable elite-clipboard.service elite-tray.service
systemctl --user start elite-clipboard.service elite-tray.service
```

**9. Verify**

```bash
ecb ping
# expected: [+]  daemon is alive
```

