## CLI

```
ecb search  [query]    Search clipboard history
ecb ws      <0-4>      List items in a workspace
ecb pin     <id>       Pin an item permanently
ecb unpin   <id>       Unpin an item
ecb del     <id>       Soft-delete an item
ecb copy    <id>       Push item back to clipboard
ecb clear   [ws]       Clear history, optionally by workspace
ecb pinned             List all pinned items
ecb ping               Check daemon status
```

