## Workspaces

| ID | Name      | Cap | Retention |
|----|-----------|-----|-----------|
| 0  | Work      | 200 | 30 days   |
| 1  | Code      | 300 | 60 days   |
| 2  | Research  | 200 | 30 days   |
| 3  | Temp      | 50  | 1 day     |
| 4  | Sensitive | 50  | 1 day     |

