## Configuration

Auto-generated at `~/.config/elite-clipboard/config.json`:

```json
{
  "max_items": 500,
  "size_cap_mb": 100,
  "poll_interval_ms": 1000,
  "monitor_clipboard": true,
  "monitor_primary": false,
  "min_content_length": 4,
  "excluded_apps": ["keepassxc", "KeePassXC", "gnome-keyring"]
}
```

