## Uninstall

```bash
systemctl --user stop elite-clipboard.service elite-tray.service
systemctl --user disable elite-clipboard.service elite-tray.service
rm ~/.config/systemd/user/elite-clipboard.service
rm ~/.config/systemd/user/elite-tray.service
sudo rm /usr/local/bin/ecb /usr/local/bin/elite-clipd /usr/local/bin/ecb-pick
rm -rf ~/elite-clipboard ~/.config/elite-clipboard ~/.local/share/elite-clipboard
rm -f ~/.local/share/applications/elite-clipboard.desktop
```

